Metadata: (6"R",7"S")-​7-​Amino-​7,8-​dihydro-​"alpha"-​bisabolene, an antimicrobial metabolite from the marine sponge "Halichondria" sp

The authors report the isolation of the antimicrobial metabolite (6"R",7"S")-​7-​amino-​7,8-​dihydro-​"alpha"-​bisabolene, its hydrochloride salt, the corresponding urea and isothiocyanate, and an unrelated sesquiterpene hydrocarbon from the sponge "Halichondria" sp.
